      "span_text": "The multiple regression analysis (MRA) remains the most reliable automated valuation method, which was successfully applied, among other things, in constructing price indices in Geneva, Switzerland, determining rental values in Bordeaux, France, explaining the market in Tel Aviv, Israel."
